injuries.comment: The Cavaliers announced that Thomas is continuing to rehabilitate and they are hopeful he will be able to return by January.
Cavaliers announced James will play in Tuesday's (Oct 17) regular season opener.
Yabusele has been ruled Out for Tuesday's (Oct 17) regular season opener.
Baynes has resumed practicing in full and barring setbacks will play in Tuesday's (Oct 17) season opener against the Cavaliers, according to the Boston Herald.
Morris is expected to miss the first three games of the season, according to Chris Forsberg of ESPN.
